import React, {useState, useEffect} from "react";

import { View, Text, TextInput, Button } from 'react-native';

const MapForm = () => {
  return (
    <View>
      <Text>Create Map</Text>
      <TextInput
        className="name"
        type="text"
        placeholder="Name"
      />
      <TextInput
        className="id"
        type="text"
        placeholder="Site id"
      />
      <TextInput
        className="description"
        type="text"
        placeholder="Description"
      />
      <TextInput
        className="level"
        type="text"
        placeholder="Level"
      />
      <TextInput
      className = "fielName"
      type = "text"
      placeholder = "File Name"
    />
    <TextInput
    className = "qrCode"
    type = "text"
    placeholder = "QR Code in here "
  />


    </View>
  );
};


export default MapForm;
